{"tid":2065224,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"閉門賽超靜 軒達臣驚爆粗出醜","createTime":"2020-06-15T11:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T15:06:12.000Z","uid":322766,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"30be67bb0c8d773129a9b25edb20970931ccaeae","tid":2065224,"uid":322766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:45:53.000Z","msg":"英超即將重啟，利物浦隊長佐敦軒達臣表示要適應閉門賽環境，盡量減少講粗口。<br />\n<br />\n由於沒有現場觀眾，所以比賽時環境安靜，令攝影機收音非常清楚，球員及領隊在場上所說的話都無所遁形。<br />\n<br />\n佐敦軒達臣（Jordan Henderson）笑言很擔心忍不住在數以千萬計的家庭觀眾面前爆粗：「我不想每場比賽之後都要向各位道歉，所以真的要小心，特別是比賽很緊張的情況下。」<br />\n<br />\n這名英格蘭國腳中場更拉領隊高普落水：「我肯定他也要小心！不過，他也知道我們不能夠因此怪責沒有現場觀眾。」<br />\n<br />\n利物浦現時於英超領放25分，只要多拿6分就能夠首奪冠軍，軒達臣表示要克服閉門賽環境：「我們小時候為學校出戰也沒有觀眾，這樣你更能享受足球。我們要在既有的情況下交出最佳表現。」<br />\n<br />\nFrom now sports<br />\n<em><a href=\"https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=29806736853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D29806736853&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=1563f704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=29806736853</a></em>"},{"pid":"9cff2f31ae4560c39cb6e2597708e5c6457aacc1","tid":2065224,"uid":525,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"平常心啦神軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4489e8241f6901d0052f2a7fa445ad66188b1ad5","tid":2065224,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:51:11.000Z","msg":"軒達臣gif"},{"pid":"eea4ae8b4fec2109903b1f10b7ee385cd1152757","tid":2065224,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:53:41.000Z","msg":"學德甲配音囉"},{"pid":"1448379911897c7208fb603ae56a52c00d80c1d7","tid":2065224,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"佢屌開邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9a201631b24a2f9342c61efc87